'''澳洲氣象局'''（{{lang-en|Bureau of Meteorology}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]作'''BOM'''）<ref name="au" />，前身為'''中央氣象局'''<ref>{{cite web |url = http://media.bom.gov.au/social/blog/21/the-first-commonwealth-meteorologist-the-farsighted-legacy-of-henry-a-hunt/ |title = The first Commonwealth Meteorologist: the farsighted legacy of Henry A. Hunt |publisher = Bureau of Meteorology |date = 7 February 2012 |accessdate = 17 October 2014 |language = en |archive-date = 2021-03-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210314080439/http://media.bom.gov.au/social/blog/21/the-first-commonwealth-meteorologist-the-farsighted-legacy-of-henry-a-hunt/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，是澳大利亚联邦政府的一個行政機構負責向澳大利亞和周邊地區提供氣象服務。根據《氣象法》成立於1906年，並匯聚在此之前存在的國家氣象服務。1908年1月1日，各州正式移交他們的天氣記錄責任予澳洲氣象局<ref name="ABC">{{cite web |url = http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2008/01/01/2129737.htm |title = BOM celebrates 100 years |publisher = Australian Broadcasting Corporation |accessdate = 1 January 2008 |language = en |archive-date = 2012-09-22 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6As5L5WGu?url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2008-01-01/bom-celebrates-100-years/1000082 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title = Collections in Perth: 20. Meteorology |publisher = National Archives of Australia |date =  |url = http://www.naa.gov.au/naaresources/Publications/research_guides/guides/perth/chapter20.htm |accessdate = 24 May 2008 |language = en |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6As5Lw1K2?url=http://www.naa.gov.au/naaresources/Publications/research_guides/guides/perth/chapter20.htm |archive-date = 2012-09-22 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

